headline: Texas Pacific: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: DALLAS (AP) — Texas Pacific Land Corporation (TPL) on Wednesday reported net income of $123.3 million in its fourth quarter. On a per-share basis, the Dallas-based company said it had net income of $1.79. The landowner posted revenue of $211.6 million in the period.
